                    verified by Blockchain Technology</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row no-gutters">
            <div class="col-lg-6 text-white showcase-img"
                style="background-image: url('images/landing-page/interview.jpg');"></div>
            <div class="col-lg-6 my-auto showcase-text">
                <h2>For Employers</h2>
                <p class="lead mb-0">Rest assured that degrees shared with you on our platform are authentic and require
