                    Onboard new hires faster rather than wait for them to verify their credenitials.
                    Seamless. Fast. Faster hiring cycles. Instantenous. Less administrative costs and follow up
                    communication with applicants.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row no-gutters">
            <div class="col-lg-6 order-lg-2 text-white showcase-img"
                style="background-image: url('images/landing-page/degree.jpg');"></div>
            <div class="col-lg-6 order-lg-1 my-auto showcase-text">
                <h2>For Universities</h2>
                <p class="lead mb-0">Improves the verifiabilty and authenticity of awarded degrees internationally! Join
